articles.author: Charles Bradley
articles.title: F1 results: Charles Leclerc fastest in Hungarian GP practice - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Ferrari’s Charles Leclerc was fastest in Hungarian Grand Prix practice in Budapest, ahead of the 12th round of the 2023 Formula 1 World Championship.
articles.content: George Russells Mercedes was quickest in a rain-impacted Free Practice 1, before Leclerc set the fastest time of the day in a dry FP2 at 1m17.686s, 0.015s quicker than Lando Norris (McLaren) and Pier… [+2328 chars]
